title: Ypsolopha lonicerella
text:
Ypsolopha lonicerella is a <a href="moth">moth</a> of the family <a href="Ypsolophidae">Ypsolophidae</a>. It is known to be found in the eastern part of the <a href="Carpathian%20Mountains">Carpathian Mountains</a>.
The <a href="wingspan">wingspan</a> is about 18–20 mm.
